<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .header {
            
            background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #c158da 10%, #56b67f 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .user-info {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .user-info p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to [Company Name]</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="logo" style="display: flex; justify-content:flex-end;align-itmes:center">
                <img style="max-width: 180px;max-height:50px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:0;" src='https://res.cloudinary.com/ddzwtjgkt/image/upload/v1719816499/DigitalMarketing/k3msq4bcek4swmzh1zle.png' alt="logo" />
            </div>
            <p><strong>Hello {{clientName}},</strong></p>
            
            <p>Thanks for choosing our platform. We are glad to have you with us now. Let's take a step ahead toward a bright future.</p>
            <p>Your login credentials are:</p>
            <div class="user-info">
                
                <p><strong>Username:</strong> {{clientUserName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{password}}</p>
            </div>
            <p>Please keep your login details secure.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br> <strong>[company name here]</strong> </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
